snippet.title: Battle Princess Madelyn Trailer
snippet.description:
Do you have what it takes to save your family and kingdom? Do you have what it takes to avenge your loyal companion?  Join Battle Princess Madelyn on her quest to become the ultimate knight! 

Coming this fall to Nintendo Switch, Playstation 4, Xbox One, Steam and more!
